Gotron/Zava

A cargo ship lands in Northern Africa. Two bots, who had just 
travelled from Cybertron step out, and begin DNA Scanning. The ships 
scanners find two acceptable matches. When Scanning the mountains, it 
finds a Goat. When searching the plains, it comes across a Zebra. The 
bots are given there forms. They exit the ship.

"Ha ha! Finaly, Gotron has arrived!!!!!"

"Oh shut up!"

"Be quiet Zava. Now, where are you going?"

"I'm gonna go find Deemos and The Chosne Ones. All that destruction! 
Thanks for the ride, Gotron. Maybe see you again someday."

Zava took off to find the Chosen Ones.

"Good, she's gone. Now to finish the job and join The Alliance!"

Gotrn pulled out his rocket launcher and fired continually at his 
ship. It blew up in a huge explosion of fire.

"No one is getting off this planet now!"

Gotrn takes off heading for the Alliance base.
